# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:38
translate spanish hwb_s12c_5bbb1c60:

    # "Vast and majestic, the canyon dominates the horizon, as far as my eyes can see. Calico rocks are given a murky tint by the dying sunlight."
    "Vasto y majestuoso, el cañón domina el horizonte, hasta donde alcanza mi vista. Las rocas de tonos calicó adquieren un tinte sombrío por la luz moribunda del sol."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:40
translate spanish hwb_s12c_83a92d3d:

    # "It’s a breathtaking view. I just stare out over the abyss, watching as the sun slowly climbs down the sky."
    "Es una vista impresionante. Solo me quedo mirando el abismo, observando cómo el sol desciende lentamente por el cielo."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:45
translate spanish hwb_s12c_94d3e8ad:

    # Mariah "What are you even looking at."
    Mariah "На что ты вообще там смотришь."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:49
translate spanish hwb_s12c_9c979997:

    # "She says it flatly, not like a question. Mariah’s been this way for hours now, since Joseph practically dragged her out of the RV."
    "Lo dice de manera plana, no como una pregunta. Mariah ha estado así durante horas, desde que Joseph prácticamente la arrastró fuera de la casa rodante."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:51
translate spanish hwb_s12c_2adaf5ab:

    # "While the other three have amused themselves with disposable cameras and curiosity, Mariah’s tailed me like a mangy dog."
    "Mientras los otros tres se han entretenido con cámaras desechables y curiosidad, Mariah me ha seguido como un perro sarnoso."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:53
translate spanish hwb_s12c_7099add7:

    # "She won’t let me forget about her relentless apathy, punctuating it with frequent sighs."
    "No me deja olvidar su implacable apatía, puntuándola con frecuentes suspiros."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:57
translate spanish hwb_s12c_4845789d:

    # Amber "I’m looking at the cliffs. And considering sending you to get a closer look at the bottom."
    Amber "Я смотрю на обрывы. И подумываю скинуть тебя оттуда, чтобы ты получше рассмотрела, что там внизу."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:62
translate spanish hwb_s12c_71d153a9:

    # Mariah "This is your fault, you know."
    Mariah "Это все из-за тебя, знаешь ли."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:66
translate spanish hwb_s12c_cbcda6c9:

    # Amber "What is?"
    Amber "Ты о чем?"

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:70
translate spanish hwb_s12c_eec650db:

    # Mariah "That we’re here. Or at least that I’m here."
    Mariah "Что мы здесь. Или что, по крайней мере, я здесь."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:74
translate spanish hwb_s12c_b5530b23:

    # Amber "Hey, I didn’t want you along either. That was all Marina."
    Amber "Эй, я вообще-то тоже не хотела, чтобы ты была тут. Это все Марина."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:76
translate spanish hwb_s12c_94bb66b5:

    # Mariah "Just tell that airhead ‘no’ sometime. Guessing you’ve never turned down a request of hers in your life."
    Mariah "Просто научись иногда говорить «нет» этой пустоголовой. Полагаю, ты ни разу в жизни не отказывал ей ни в чем."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:78
translate spanish hwb_s12c_7b7b84fd:

    # "I shoot her a dirty look at the word ‘airhead.’"
    "Le lanzo una mirada de desaprobación ante la palabra 'cabeza hueca'."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:80
translate spanish hwb_s12c_32991802:

    # "Mariah rolls her eyes. She doesn't care one bit."
    "Mariah pone los ojos en blanco. No le importa ni un poco."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:84
translate spanish hwb_s12c_f9e25e99:

    # Amber "She wanted to play with Tess. Someone has to."
    Amber "Она просто хотела поиграть с Тесс. Хоть кто-то же должен."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:86
translate spanish hwb_s12c_6cbadc5f:

    # Mariah "Joe does it all the time."
    Mariah "Джо постоянно делает это."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:88
translate spanish hwb_s12c_903be0bd:

    # "Her ability to miss the point is actually kind of impressive."
    "Su habilidad para no captar el punto es en realidad bastante impresionante."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:90
translate spanish hwb_s12c_73917ce6:

    # Amber "Besides, you should see the look I get if I try to stop her from something. Maybe I can’t say no."
    Amber "Кроме того, тебе стоит видеть, какой взгляд я получаю от нее каждый раз, когда я пытаюсь остановить ее. Может, я не могу сказать «нет»."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:94
translate spanish hwb_s12c_7e080d4e:

    # Mariah "Be more like me. Mental fortitude and training."
    Mariah "Будь такой, как я. Нужна лишь стойкость и сила духа."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:98
translate spanish hwb_s12c_39674b60:

    # Amber "Is almost breaking down when someone threatens to take away the key to your liquor cabinet part of that 'mental fortitude and training?'"
    Amber "А может ли это считаться «стойкостью и силой духа» или все же срывом, когда кто-то грозится украсть ключ от твоего мини-бара?"

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:104
translate spanish hwb_s12c_59d6cfae:

    # "She clicks her tongue in annoyance and grumbles."
    "Chasquea la lengua con molestia y refunfuña."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:106
translate spanish hwb_s12c_57d26e25:

    # Mariah "I could have still said no. I was just doing it for Tess."
    Mariah "Я ведь могла сказать «нет». Я согласилась на это только ради Тесс."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:133
translate spanish hwb_s12c_13b032e1:

    # "I turn my attention over to the impromptu photoshoot again."
    "Vuelvo a prestar atención a la sesión de fotos improvisada."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:135
translate spanish hwb_s12c_8e69fead:

    # "Both the girls climb on the rocks and lean against the railings to take pictures. Joseph trails close behind, probably to make sure nobody slips. Sometimes, he’s pulled in for a picture too."
    "Ambas chicas se suben a las rocas y se apoyan en las barandillas para tomar fotos. Joseph las sigue de cerca, probablemente para asegurarse de que nadie resbale. A veces, también lo arrastran para una foto."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:137
translate spanish hwb_s12c_e0cd7759:

    # "Marina’s taken pictures of just about everything. The sky, the ground, a pouting Mariah. As a photographer, she’s not very picky."
    "Marina ha tomado fotos de casi todo. El cielo, el suelo, una Mariah enfurruñada. Como fotógrafa, no es muy exigente."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:139
translate spanish hwb_s12c_064d0b7a:

    # "Tess, on the other hand, seems to have an actual knack for it. She’s taken pictures of scenic valleys and closeups of beautiful desert flowers in full bloom, usually with Joseph as the model."
    "Tess, por otro lado, parece tener un verdadero talento para ello. Ha tomado fotos de valles escénicos y primeros planos de hermosas flores del desierto en plena floración, generalmente con Joseph como modelo."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:141
translate spanish hwb_s12c_150b5c62:

    # "She even managed to get close enough to take one of an eagle perched on a rock."
    "Incluso logró acercarse lo suficiente para tomar una foto de un águila posada en una roca."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:145
translate spanish hwb_s12c_e51d3757:

    # "Not hard when you’re practically invisible, though."
    "No es difícil cuando eres prácticamente invisible, la verdad."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:161
translate spanish hwb_s12c_ab20b098:

    # Mariah "I don’t even know why she’s so interested in this stuff."
    Mariah "Даже не понимаю, почему она так сильно увлечена этим."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:166
translate spanish hwb_s12c_02f947bc:

    # Amber "What, the wonder and majesty of naturally formed geographic wonders?"
    Amber "Ты о ее восхищении величественными творениями природы?"

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:168
translate spanish hwb_s12c_4c54c70f:

    # Mariah "That’s a fancy way of saying 'overgrown rocks.'"
    Mariah "Какое вычурное название для переросших камней."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:170
translate spanish hwb_s12c_b2db2b90:

    # Amber "Who cares? Shouldn’t you be glad that she is?"
    Amber "Да какая разница? Разве ты не рада ее увлечению?"

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:172
translate spanish hwb_s12c_0819612c:

    # Mariah "Why? I’d prefer if she cared about something that matters."
    Mariah "С чего бы? Я бы предпочла, чтобы она была увлечена чем-то более важным."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:176
translate spanish hwb_s12c_7d75f2b8:

    # Amber "Like getting rich?"
    Amber "Например, тем, как разбогатеть?"

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:181
translate spanish hwb_s12c_8e60a1ba:

    # Mariah "Exactly."
    Mariah "Именно."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:194
translate spanish hwb_s12c_48ba6c4b:

    # Mariah "{cps=80}It’s {w=0.3}'Americana this, {w=0.8}sightseeing that.' {w=1.0}What the hell even is Americana?{/cps}"
    Mariah "{cps=80}It”s {w=0.3} «Почувствуй Американу, {w=0.8}смотри кругом.» {w=1.0} Да что за хрень эта Американа?{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:198
translate spanish hwb_s12c_a68b66a5:

    # Mariah "'Don’t mess with Texas' shirts and old rocking chairs that some hicks farted on?"
    Mariah "Футболки с надписью «Не грози Техасу» и старые кресла-качалки, которые пропахли пердежом деревенщин?"

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:204
translate spanish hwb_s12c_aaca9891:

    # Amber "Do you ever listen to yourself talk? Just be happy she’s interested in culture and expanding her horizons."
    Amber "Ты вообще слушаешь, что ты говоришь? Просто будь счастлива, что она интересуется культурой и расширением своего кругозора."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:208
translate spanish hwb_s12c_704f1727:

    # Mariah "Culture? Hah! Our favorite foods are bastardized versions of foreign cuisine."
    Mariah "Культурой? Хах! Наши любимые блюда – это извращенные подражания иностранной кухне."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:212
translate spanish hwb_s12c_234c7348:

    # Mariah "Culture’s a sham."
    Mariah "Эта культура – притворство."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:216
translate spanish hwb_s12c_2683972a:

    # Mariah "When I was her age, I was interested in things that actually mattered{w=1.0}—like treasure!"
    Mariah "Когда я была в ее возрасте, я интересовалась более значимыми вещами{w=1.0}—например, сокровищами!"

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:226
translate spanish hwb_s12c_e6fb7f62:

    # Joseph "Years later and nothing’s changed."
    Joseph "Годы идут, и ничего не меняется."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:230
translate spanish hwb_s12c_94c82785:

    # "Since the other girls are taking a break, Joseph has joined us."
    "Como las otras chicas están tomando un descanso, Joseph se nos ha unido."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:232
translate spanish hwb_s12c_a077ce05:

    # Joseph "They wanna take some pictures with you."
    Joseph "Они хотят несколько фотографий с вами."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:238
translate spanish hwb_s12c_d3b7f3cd:

    # "Mariah starts to protest, {w=0.8}but Joseph cuts her off."
    "Mariah empieza a protestar, {w=0.8}pero Joseph la interrumpe."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:240
translate spanish hwb_s12c_04c6283d:

    # Joseph "Your sister wanted me to ask."
    Joseph "Твоя сестра попросила сказать тебе это."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:244
translate spanish hwb_s12c_7792c2e5:

    # "Her mouth shuts, and she rolls her eyes yet again."
    "Ella cierra la boca y vuelve a poner los ojos en blanco."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:248
translate spanish hwb_s12c_d0b90fed:

    # Mariah "Fine."
    Mariah "Ладно."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:255
translate spanish hwb_s12c_a04abb21:

    # "She stalks over to where they are, kicking up clouds of dust with each heavy step."
    "Se acerca a donde están ellas, levantando nubes de polvo con cada paso pesado."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:260
translate spanish hwb_s12c_be335bf4:

    # Joseph "Sorry if she's causing you trouble. She can be a bit of a handful."
    Joseph "Прости, если она доставляет тебе неудобства. Она может быть слегка проблематичной."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:264
translate spanish hwb_s12c_5c0926a2:

    # Joseph "I know it’s hard to believe, but there's a good heart in there... somewhere."
    Joseph "Я знаю, в это трудно поверить, но у нее есть доброе сердце… Где-то глубоко внутри."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:269
translate spanish hwb_s12c_b825633e:

    # Amber "She’d probably sell it for a dollar if she could."
    Amber "Она бы наверняка продала его за доллар, если бы могла."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:273
translate spanish hwb_s12c_cdfab8f0:

    # "Joseph laughs heartily."
    "Joseph se ríe a carcajadas."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:275
translate spanish hwb_s12c_83034ca5:

    # Joseph "You might be right."
    Joseph "Возможно ты права."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:279
translate spanish hwb_s12c_ae264f50:

    # Joseph "That’s just how she is, I guess. Been that way since we were kids."
    Joseph "Такой уж у нее характер, полагаю. Он был таким у нее с самого нашего детства."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:281
translate spanish hwb_s12c_7ea82767:

    # "It's hard to imagine that someone could not only know Mariah as a child, but want to maintain a friendship with her for the rest of their lives."
    "Es difícil imaginar que alguien no solo haya conocido a Mariah de niña, sino que quiera mantener una amistad con ella por el resto de su vida."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:283
translate spanish hwb_s12c_30e1f316:

    # "Come to think of it, Joseph’s a bit of an odd case compared to the other two. Odd just because he’s so normal."
    "Ahora que lo pienso, Joseph es un caso un poco extraño comparado con las otras dos. Extraño solo porque es tan normal."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:287
translate spanish hwb_s12c_356c4a05:

    # Amber "Hey, can I ask you something?"
    Amber "Эй, могу ли я спросить тебя о кое-чем?"

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:289
translate spanish hwb_s12c_fa3c1363:

    # Joseph "Shoot."
    Joseph "Валяй."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:293
translate spanish hwb_s12c_3eaeef8d:

    # Amber "Do you care about the treasure?"
    Amber "Ты же хочешь найти сокровище?"

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:297
translate spanish hwb_s12c_aef03e6d:

    # "He scratches the stubble on his chin and thinks about it."
    "Se rasca la barba incipiente en la barbilla y lo piensa."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:299
translate spanish hwb_s12c_c38eb430:

    # Amber "Like, you have a good head on your shoulders. Why do you let her drag you around?"
    Amber "У тебя же, вроде, есть своя голова на плечах. Почему ты позволяешь Марии втягивать себя в это?"

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:303
translate spanish hwb_s12c_7a6b882c:

    # Joseph "Well, it's not that I don't care about the treasure. Being rich doesn’t sound like a bad gig at all."
    Joseph "Ну, не то чтобы меня так уж волнует это сокровище. Однако стать богатым кажется вполне себе неплохой перспективой."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:305
translate spanish hwb_s12c_08355e41:

    # Joseph "But I wouldn't say I have a good head on my shoulders, either. If it came down to treasure hunting or kicking back on a couch all day, I’d pick the couch."
    Joseph "Но я бы и не сказал, что у меня такая уж светлая голова, как ты думаешь. Если бы передо мной стоял выбор отправиться на поиски сокровищ или проваляться весь день на диване, я бы выбрал второе."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:309
translate spanish hwb_s12c_430c4cab:

    # Amber "Figures."
    Amber "Кто бы сомневался."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:313
translate spanish hwb_s12c_da8b1216:

    # "His own broad smile returns. I didn’t even notice it disappear."
    "Su propia sonrisa amplia regresa. Ni siquiera noté que había desaparecido."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:315
translate spanish hwb_s12c_043f29ca:

    # Joseph "But as for them."
    Joseph "А что касается их."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:317
translate spanish hwb_s12c_193296c0:

    # Joseph "One of them needs someone to look out for her, and the other is ten."
    Joseph "Одной из них нужно, чтобы за ней кто-то постоянно приглядывал, а другой всего десять лет."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:321
translate spanish hwb_s12c_96b0a4b2:

    # "Now we both laugh."
    "Ahora nos reímos los dos."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:325
translate spanish hwb_s12c_b8ac9ae0:

    # Joseph "If she’s the one who gets me off the couch, I’m the one who gets her to sit down sometimes."
    Joseph "Если она та самая, кто заставляет меня подниматься с дивана, то я тот, кто усаживает ее туда хоть иногда."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:327
translate spanish hwb_s12c_6800190a:

    # Joseph "Even back in school, she was always picking fights. Didn’t matter if it was with another kid or a teacher."
    Joseph "Даже когда она еще училась в школе, она всегда находила себе проблемы. Не важно с кем, с другим ребенком или с учителем."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:329
translate spanish hwb_s12c_b6c5d49f:

    # Joseph "Got her ass kicked a couple times. If she were all on her own, she’d tear apart the whole Southwest."
    Joseph "Ей надирали задницу пару раз. Но если бы она была сама по себе в этой поездке, она бы разнесла весь юго-запад."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:333
translate spanish hwb_s12c_a922aa75:

    # Joseph "That make sense?"
    Joseph "Так что все логично, правда?"

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:335
translate spanish hwb_s12c_5a30597f:

    # "I look over at where the three of them are still taking pictures. Tess is standing on a rock so that she’s at the same level as the others."
    "Miro hacia donde las tres siguen tomándose fotos. Tess está parada sobre una roca para estar al mismo nivel que las demás."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:337
translate spanish hwb_s12c_9ac528da:

    # "Right now, two of her fingers hold Mariah’s mouth into the shape of a smile. On Mariah’s other side, Marina holds the camera out and takes their picture."
    "En este momento, dos de sus dedos sostienen la boca de Mariah en forma de sonrisa. Al otro lado de Mariah, Marina sostiene la cámara y les toma la foto."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:339
translate spanish hwb_s12c_3f1de217:

    # "Then Tess takes one, though Marina keeps her hand out of Mariah’s mouth."
    "Luego Tess toma una, aunque Marina mantiene su mano fuera de la boca de Mariah."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:343
translate spanish hwb_s12c_d46b4c3c:

    # Amber "Yeah, I know what you mean."
    Amber "Да, я поняла, что ты имеешь в виду."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:347
translate spanish hwb_s12c_afcbd69c:

    # Joseph "Plus, someone’s gotta make sure Tess doesn’t starve."
    Joseph "Кроме того, кто-то же должен следить за тем, чтобы Тесс не не приходилось голодать."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:349
translate spanish hwb_s12c_d4143871:

    # "Catching us watching, Marina waves vigorously. She nearly knocks Mariah’s lights out while she does. I wave back."
    "Al vernos mirando, Marina saluda vigorosamente. Casi noquea a Mariah mientras lo hace. Le devuelvo el saludo."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:351
translate spanish hwb_s12c_81b444d4:

    # "Tess says something that gets Marina’s attention, and after a second Marina hurries over. I wince as I watch her clumsily climb over the rocks, scared that she’s going to slip and hurt herself."
    "Tess dice algo que capta la atención de Marina, y después de un segundo, Marina se apresura. Hago una mueca mientras la veo trepar torpemente las rocas, temiendo que resbale y se lastime."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:360
translate spanish hwb_s12c_aa1b078e:

    # "But she arrives unharmed."
    "Pero llega ilesa."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:362
translate spanish hwb_s12c_583a3c7e:

    # Marina "Tess wanted me to ask if you’d go be in the pictures too, Joe. She says she wants all three of you."
    Marina "Тесс попросила меня спросить у тебя, не хочешь ли ты тоже пофотографироваться, Джо. Она сказала, что хочет, чтобы все трое из вас были вместе."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:368
translate spanish hwb_s12c_8d647187:

    # Joseph "Looks like that’s my cue."
    Joseph "Похоже, что настал мой час."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:384
translate spanish hwb_s12c_998c8aec:

    # "With nothing more to say, he drifts over to the others and exchanges spots with Marina."
    "Sin nada más que decir, se acerca a las demás e intercambia lugar con Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:386
translate spanish hwb_s12c_d7f1228a:

    # "Tess passes him the camera, and he holds it up to his eye."
    "Tess le pasa la cámara, y él la sostiene frente a su ojo."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:390
translate spanish hwb_s12c_721b2835:

    # Joseph "Why are you using this cheap thing anyway? The camera on Mariah's phone is way better."
    Joseph "Почему вы вообще пользуетесь этим дешевым фотиком? Камера на телефоне Марии и то будет лучше."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:392
translate spanish hwb_s12c_e26cc1a0:

    # "He takes the camera from Tess and dangles from his fingers, observing it like it's an ancient, long buried artifact."
    "Toma la cámara de Tess y la deja colgar de sus dedos, observándola como si fuera un antiguo artefacto enterrado por mucho tiempo."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:400
translate spanish hwb_s12c_5881192a:

    # Tess "The memory is full from all her journal entries."
    Tess "Память телефона заполнена ее записями в заметках."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:404
translate spanish hwb_s12c_0b67ff37:

    # Amber "Journal?"
    Amber "Заметки?"

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:408
translate spanish hwb_s12c_b7098257:

    # Tess "It's more like angsty poetry."
    Tess "Больше похоже на унылые стишки."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:416
translate spanish hwb_s12c_25d7d872:

    # "Mariah turns toward me, panic and fury in her eyes, but she’s too slow."
    "Mariah se gira hacia mí, con pánico y furia en los ojos, pero es demasiado lenta."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:420
translate spanish hwb_s12c_c72ef414:

    # Joseph "How did that one go again?"
    Joseph "Как же там было..."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:424
translate spanish hwb_s12c_ca4ccecc:

    # Joseph "Oh yeah!"
    Joseph "О да!"

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:434
translate spanish hwb_s12c_977af3c9:

    # Joseph "\"Rivers of amber pour from my bottle like tears, {w=0.7}forever sweeping El Dorado beyond my grasp.\""
    Joseph "“Янтарные реки льются из сосуда словно слезы, {w=0.7} навеки унося Эльдорадо туда, где мне его не достать”."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:436
translate spanish hwb_s12c_b5ca916f:

    # "Mariah slouches."
    "Mariah se encorva."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:440
translate spanish hwb_s12c_b2478d5b:

    # Mariah "I hate you both."
    Mariah "Я ненавижу вас обоих."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:444
translate spanish hwb_s12c_2d014aa2:

    # Joseph "Aww, but we love you, Mariah."
    Joseph "Оуу, а мы любим тебя, Мария."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:449
translate spanish hwb_s12c_fc76c63a:

    # "Tess clings to her sister’s waist like a magnet, showing her affection."
    "Tess se aferra a la cintura de su hermana como un imán, mostrando su afecto."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:451
translate spanish hwb_s12c_50a50e3c:

    # "It goes ignored."
    "Es ignorado."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:453
translate spanish hwb_s12c_6905838a:

    # Joseph "Now squeeze in, I'm not sure how we're all gonna fit."
    Joseph "А теперь прижмитесь поплотнее."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:466
translate spanish hwb_s12c_7debee43:

    # "We watch for a moment, before I tap Marina on the shoulder."
    "Observamos por un momento, antes de que toque a Marina en el hombro."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:468
translate spanish hwb_s12c_63851b5b:

    # "That should keep them busy for a while."
    "Eso debería mantenerlos ocupados por un rato."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:474
translate spanish hwb_s12c_e4b07212:

    # Amber "Quick! While they’re distracted!"
    Amber "Быстрее! Пока они отвлеклись!"

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:478
translate spanish hwb_s12c_07255102:

    # Mariah "Wh-{w=0.4}What—"
    Mariah "Чт-{w=0.4}Что…"

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:485
translate spanish hwb_s12c_1bc4c0de:

    # "I grab Marina’s hand and dash off, dragging her behind me, Her feet have trouble keeping up, but I don’t slow down. I don’t look back."
    "Tomo la mano de Marina y salgo corriendo, arrastrándola detrás de mí. Sus pies tienen problemas para seguirme el ritmo, pero no reduzco la velocidad. No miro atrás."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:487
translate spanish hwb_s12c_351cde5e:

    # Amber "Just keep running."
    Amber "Просто продолжай бежать."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:489
translate spanish hwb_s12c_7cf0acbb:

    # Marina "Amber, {w=0.5}where are we {cps=10}goooooooooooo{/cps}ing?"
    Marina "Эмбер, {w=0.5}куда мы {cps=10}бежиииииии{/cps}им?"

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:392
translate spanish hwb_s12c_cb9b144e:

    # "He takes the camera from Tess and dangles it from his fingers, observing it like it's an ancient, long buried artifact."
    "Él toma la cámara de Tess y la balancea con los dedos, observándola como si fuera un artefacto antiguo y enterrado hace mucho tiempo."

# game/script/hwb_s12c.rpy:478
translate spanish hwb_s12c_278bc573:

    # Marina "Wh-{w=0.4}What—"
    Marina "Чт-{w=0.4}Что…"

